the match:"I am really happy that I scored. It was a very good
second half for both teams but in the last minute we got the goal
and the whole team is happy."
</P>
<P>
"All we can do in these situations is to keep on plugging away
and in the end it paid off." added Vastic. Austria have scored
last-minute equalizer in both their group matches.
</P>
<P>
