Kogi State in the central part of the country, the News Agency of
Nigeria reported Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
A source at the Ministry of Solid Minerals Development was
quoted as saying that officials of the ministry's Geological
Survey Department were currently carrying out exploration work
for uranium deposits in parts of the state.
</P>
<P>
