Sezgin said he was glad that the two countries were making
joint efforts to combat organized crimes, terrorism and drugs
trafficking.
</P>
<P>
Referring to their diplomatic row last year, the Turkish
official said that such dispute should be prevented in the future.
</P>
<P>
