<HEADLINE> People's Daily Hails Opening of 14th National Congress of CYLC </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, June 18 (Xinhua) -- An editorial to be published on
Friday's People's Daily hails the opening of the 14th National
Congress of the Communist Youth League of China (CYLC) on the same
day.
</P>
<P>
The congress, held at a crucial stage of China's reform and
opening-up drive, is of great importance to an all-round
advancement of the great cause of building socialism with Chinese
characteristics into the 21st century, the editorial states.
</P>
<P>
The editorial says that the five years since the convocation of
the 13th National Congress of CYLC were the extraordinary years in
Chinese history, which have demonstrated that the Chinese younger
generation is a promising generation and is capable of shouldering
the great cause of building socialism with Chinese characteristics.
</P>
<P>
The Chinese younger generation should take pains to study hard
on Marxism-Leninism, Mao Zedong Thought, and especially the Deng
Xiaoping Theory, the editorial says. The study of the theory
should be aimed to solve practical problems cropped up during the
course of China's reform, opening-up and modernization drive.
</P>
<P>
As the younger generation are at a critical period of fostering
their correct world outlook, and outlook on life and value
concept, they should have a good grasp of these theories, which is
very helpful for them to achieve success in a complex domestic and
international environment.
</P>
<P>
Moreover, the younger generation should learn and work hard at
modern science and technology, which have been increasingly become
the powerful motive force for social development, the editorial
notes.
</P>
<P>
Acknowledging that young people are full of creativity, it says
that many major discoveries, inventions and creations in history
have been accomplished by them and international contests are, in
a sense, competitions between the creativities among the young
people worldwide.
</P>
<P>
Nevertheless, as the building of socialist market economy is an
unprecedented cause, the younger generation of the Chinese faces
an arduous but glorious task which is also a golden opportunity
for them to establish themselves.
</P>
<P>
Meanwhile, the younger generation should work hard and
assiduously in the course of building, developing and improving
socialist market economy, and the relatively complete socialist
market economic system will be built mainly through this
generation's efforts, and all younger people with aspirations and
lofty ideals should tamper themselves and perform outstanding
deeds for the accomplishment of this cause, the editorial says.
</P>
</TEXT>
