Zealand government's decision to grant visa-free access to Hong
Kong SAR passport holders.
</P>
<P>
From October 1, 1998, Hong Kong travelers holding Hong Kong SAR
or BN(O) passports will enjoy visa-free stays of up to three
months in New Zealand.
</P>
