Hong Kong's future and signifies the government's support of the
Hong Kong SAR under 'one country, two systems'," an SAR government
spokesman said here Thursday.
</P>
<P>
New Zealand is a popular destination for Hong Kong travelers.
More than 30,000 Hong Kong residents visited the country in 1997.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman added that New Zealand nationals will continue to
enjoy visa-free stays of three months in Hong Kong. 
