<HEADLINE> Strong German Exports in April </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BONN, June 18 (Xinhua) -- Germany's exports continued their
double-digit growth to reach 83.4 billion German marks (46.8
billion U.S. dollars) in April, up 13.7 percent over April 1997,
the Federal Statistics Office in Wiesbaden reported Thursday.
