memorable 3-2 victory over Spain as they prepare for the clash with
Bulgaria.
</P>
<P>
As to the Bulgarians, the Paris stadium holds great memories for
striker Emil Kostadinov who scored a last-gasp winner to shatter
France's qualifying hopes for the World Cup finals in the United
States four years ago.
</P>
<P>
