<HEADLINE> Bangladesh to Set Up More Science Universities </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, June 18 (Xinhua) -- The Bangladeshi government has
decided to set up 12 science and technology universities and 13
polytechnic institutes in the country in phases, a leading English
newspaper here reported Thursday.
</P>
<P>
This was disclosed by Education Minister A.S.H.K. Sadek while
replying to questions in this regard in the parliament Wednesday,
the Financial Express said.
</P>
