At present, Bangladesh has 11 government and 18 non-government
universities, 14 government and 5 non-government medical colleges,
4 engineering colleges and 1,268 other colleges, and 20
polytechnic institutes, with annual university and college
enrollment of over 62,000 and 1.27 million respectively. 
