elephant training center to the sites to check the damages and
calculate the losses," Bambang said.
</P>
<P>
He said his office could only monitor certain areas considered
vulnerable to elephant attacks.
</P>
<P>
"We have difficulty catching the wild elephants due to
financial problems," he added. 
